<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,324,1916,1942]" pageId="33" pageNumber="101">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="33.[189,1398,1963,2025]" pageId="33" pageNumber="101">The specific epithet is an adjective and refers to the mountainous habitat of the new species in the Zagros Mountain Range.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
